>>>>>>> Diabetes UK's bright idea explores how Tower Hamlets CCG has increased
uptake of diabetes education, including among ‘hard to reach’ groups, by
introducing a menu of education options and using a range of methods to better
engage with healthcare professionals and people with diabetes.
